        <hr noshade size="1">
        
        <font color="white" face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica" size="2"> Pretty much I have on pages 1-2 all my general perma-memmed spell slots (Gate/FD, Deflux, Vex, CoC, Dooming Dark, ST, Fear, Splurt, e-bolt).  Pages 3-4 I have my general swap out spells( lich, augment, pet, misc DOT's, DMF, Undead Nuke, Degen).  Pages 5-6 I have some of my more obscure but more commonly used (Levant, Undead Slow, Cascading Dark, Sent, Bind etc).  The next 6 or so pages are filled with spells that I might use.  I try to keep all my old and unused spells at the end of my spell book (unused = old pets, old hp/mana spells, taps, etc).   </P><P></P><P><A target=B href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=95266" ><img src="http://www.isomedia.com/homes/kuoman/Kuotat.jpg" border=0></a><a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height=15 width=15 border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
